http://www.boost.org

Preparing: 
to get a copy of boost. please follow https://svn.boost.org/trac/boost/wiki/TryModBoost
git clone --recursive https://github.com/boostorg/boost.git $YOUR_BOOST_FOLDER_NAME
cd $YOUR_BOOST_FOLDER_NAME
./bootstrap.sh
./b2 headers

Run: run on mac
export DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH=${BOOST_ROOT}/stage/lib
http://lists.apple.com/archives/unix-porting/2002/Sep/msg00021.html